2:41 PM DA calls case and states appearances. Defendant Anne Marie Batson in court.  Attorney Karl J. Kelz in court for State of Wisconsin. DA Kelz states an agreement has been reached and recites the agreement on record. Defendant freely, voluntarily, and intelligently waives the right to an attorney. DA Kelz states all applicable Victim's Rights Legislations have been complied with. DE enters plea of NO CONTEST to the sole count. Court questions DE regarding the plea. DA explains elements of charge.  Court finds plea/waiver to be free, etc.  Court finds factual basis does exist.  Court accepts plea, finds DE guilty and orders a Deferred Entry of Judgement.
